description:
The original PR for PHPLIB-493 inadvertently preserved some obsolete code for handling an "options" argument for insertMany:

{code}
case 'insertMany':
    // Merge nested and top-level options (see: SPEC-1158)
    $options = isset($args['options']) ? (array) $args['options'] : [];
    $options += array_diff_key($args, ['documents' => 1]);

    return $collection->insertMany(
        $args['documents'],
        $options
    );
{code}

This should be removed, as no unified spec tests use an "options" argument (per [Expressing Required and Optional Parameters|https://github.com/mongodb/specifications/blob/master/source/unified-test-format/unified-test-format.rst#expressing-required-and-optional-parameters]).

